WEBVTT

00:01.201 --> 00:03.535
[ static ]

00:03.537 --> 00:07.205
♪♪

00:07.207 --> 00:12.611
♪ my dreams are all dead
and buried ♪

00:12.613 --> 00:17.215
♪ sometimes I wish the sun
would explode ♪

00:17.884 --> 00:23.021
♪ when god comes
and calls me to his kingdom ♪

00:23.023 --> 00:27.760
♪ me yo vallaro pendejos
cuando me voy ♪

00:27.762 --> 00:28.961
My turn!

00:28.963 --> 00:30.362
Hell, no!

00:30.364 --> 00:32.297
Do not touch the trim!

00:33.834 --> 00:35.834
Rusty: Now, with the "fortress
of solitude" package,

00:35.836 --> 00:38.771
Every room is covered
with glass break detectors,

00:38.773 --> 00:41.506
Motion sensors,
anti-prowler strobe lights,

00:41.508 --> 00:43.041
And hell, I'll throw
in a doorbell camera,

00:43.043 --> 00:44.042
No extra charge.

00:44.044 --> 00:45.444
That sound good to you?

00:45.446 --> 00:46.779
Rusty, there probably ain't

00:46.781 --> 00:48.647
A safer place
in the whole county

00:48.649 --> 00:51.049
Than where you're standing
right this minute.

00:51.051 --> 00:52.450
Sure, I'm a sheriff,

00:52.452 --> 00:54.787
But on the dl,
I'm a ninja, too.

00:54.789 --> 00:56.021
Hiya!

00:59.193 --> 01:01.794
Just imagine
if that was human flesh,

01:01.796 --> 01:03.462
Instead of that
damn hard oak.

01:03.464 --> 01:05.063
Well, then,
would you maybe consider

01:05.065 --> 01:06.731
The "lip service"
package?

01:06.733 --> 01:08.667
We rent you
three window stickers

01:08.669 --> 01:10.535
And a yard sign
for $4.99 a month.

01:10.537 --> 01:12.404
Now, it don't include
no monitoring,

01:12.406 --> 01:14.139
But I won't tell
nobody if you won't.

01:14.141 --> 01:15.607
Wink wink.

01:15.609 --> 01:17.476
Sorry, son, but you're trying
to sell ice

01:17.478 --> 01:18.943
To an eskimo here.

01:18.945 --> 01:21.213
Can we still say "eskimo"
in this "me too" era?

01:21.215 --> 01:24.817
Let's just go with
"native ice man."

01:24.819 --> 01:27.552
Alright, now,
I gotta get to work.

01:27.554 --> 01:28.620
Hold on a minute, sheriff.

01:28.622 --> 01:30.422
What are you hauling
in that safe?

01:30.424 --> 01:33.558
That's none
of your bees wax, rusty.

01:33.560 --> 01:36.028
But it's so valuable, you
take it to work with you?

01:36.030 --> 01:37.696
[ grunting ]

01:37.698 --> 01:39.164
Why not let halen security

01:39.166 --> 01:41.366
Turn your whole house
into a safe?

01:41.368 --> 01:43.101
[ grunting ]

01:43.103 --> 01:45.103
Then you ain't got to haul it
around everywhere.

01:45.105 --> 01:46.839
[pop! Hiss!]

01:46.841 --> 01:50.109
Alright,
show me the paperwork.

01:52.312 --> 01:54.446
8, 9, and 10!

01:54.448 --> 01:55.714
Hey, now, rusty!

01:55.716 --> 01:57.516
It looks like you made
a big sale.

01:57.518 --> 01:59.651
The full fortress
of solitude package!

01:59.653 --> 02:01.586
He even went with
the damn strobe lights.

02:01.588 --> 02:02.987
Total window dressing.

02:02.989 --> 02:06.124
[ sniffing ]
ugh, what's that smell?

02:06.126 --> 02:09.061
It's like a raccoon died
in the crawl space.

02:09.063 --> 02:10.462
Early: Well, well.

02:10.464 --> 02:13.331
A little birdie done told me
you done good this morning.

02:13.333 --> 02:17.001
And that little birdie...
Is me.

02:17.003 --> 02:18.537
Rusty, you said
this security system

02:18.539 --> 02:19.938
Was gonna keep him out.

02:19.940 --> 02:21.273
Marking your house
with these signs...

02:21.275 --> 02:22.941
You might as well tell
the whole world --

02:22.943 --> 02:24.877
"here's where the money is!"

02:24.879 --> 02:27.011
Though by the looks
of what I see in here,

02:27.013 --> 02:29.414
I ought to sue you
for false advertising.

02:29.416 --> 02:31.283
Get out.
Alright, I'm leaving.

02:31.285 --> 02:34.086
I see the sheriff's got
some of these fancy yard signs

02:34.088 --> 02:35.287
At his place, too.

02:35.289 --> 02:36.354
What do you mean by that?

02:36.356 --> 02:38.490
Security is an illusion.

02:38.492 --> 02:40.358
There's only 79 things
in this world

02:40.360 --> 02:42.094
That really
make you safe.

02:42.096 --> 02:45.830
[ whistles ]
and they're called "dogs."

02:45.832 --> 02:49.033
Ya-ya!
Whoo!

02:49.035 --> 02:51.303
I noticed you didn't
bring your safe today.

02:51.305 --> 02:54.038
Well, denny, my whole house
is a safe now,

02:54.040 --> 02:56.174
Thanks
to dan halen security.

02:56.176 --> 02:57.576
Here, check it out.

02:57.578 --> 02:58.911
20 cameras.

02:58.913 --> 03:01.380
Every one with their eyes
on the prize.

03:01.382 --> 03:02.647
[ telephone ringing ]

03:02.649 --> 03:03.716
Well, if you got
all these cameras,

03:03.718 --> 03:05.049
Why'd you chain it up?

03:05.051 --> 03:07.719
Chain?
That's not my chain!

03:07.721 --> 03:09.454
Oh, my god!
Hello?

03:09.456 --> 03:11.990
Man: Yes, we have a break-in
reported at--

03:11.992 --> 03:13.792
I know, damn it!
I just saw it!

03:13.794 --> 03:15.461
My fortress of solitude!

03:17.598 --> 03:20.799
Granny, look what I found
at sheriff's house!

03:20.801 --> 03:22.267
How you gonna open it?

03:22.269 --> 03:24.136
I got the combination
right here.

03:24.138 --> 03:25.203
Come tape this up.

03:25.205 --> 03:26.939
I don't wanna be
near the blast zone.

03:26.941 --> 03:29.274
You'd never believe
what people just leave

03:29.276 --> 03:30.342
Laying by the curb.

03:30.344 --> 03:31.810
Garbage man ain't gonna
pick up all this mess.

03:31.812 --> 03:34.012
You oughta get a medal
or something,

03:34.014 --> 03:36.748
Helping him take garbage
right out of his house.

03:36.750 --> 03:38.417
Perfectly legal, too.

03:38.419 --> 03:39.684
Yeah, I believe you.

03:39.686 --> 03:42.020
Just don't shoot
until I'm clear, okay?

03:42.022 --> 03:43.622
You got three seconds.

03:43.624 --> 03:44.957
Can you give me
three mississippis?

03:44.959 --> 03:47.626
Three utahs!
No, not utahs!

03:47.628 --> 03:48.693
Two utah!
No!

03:48.695 --> 03:50.162
One utah!

03:50.164 --> 03:52.297
Boom!

03:52.299 --> 03:54.499
You're lucky I ain't
counting with maine!

03:54.501 --> 03:55.700
Woooo-weee!

03:55.702 --> 03:56.969
Lookie, lookie,
lookie, lookie!

03:56.971 --> 03:58.837
We rich!
We rich, baby!

03:58.839 --> 04:01.039
We are richer than hell!

04:01.041 --> 04:03.508
I think.
What the hell is this?

04:03.510 --> 04:04.909
Some kinda sex thing?

04:04.911 --> 04:06.444
It's one of a kind!

04:06.446 --> 04:09.648
Ain't another one like it
anywhere in the world.

04:09.650 --> 04:11.916
What kind of poop show
are you running here?

04:11.918 --> 04:15.120
Well, uh, maybe you shouldn't
have put out that yard sign.

04:15.122 --> 04:17.122
I mean, it does kind
of tell the world,

04:17.124 --> 04:18.390
"here's where
the money is!"

04:18.392 --> 04:20.659
It wasn't money,
you dip-poop!

04:20.661 --> 04:22.995
You said impenetrable,
and on day one,

04:22.997 --> 04:25.664
My most valuable
possession, gone.

04:25.666 --> 04:27.599
Damn.
It was definitely somebody

04:27.601 --> 04:28.933
Who knew the system.

04:28.935 --> 04:30.268
The sheriff's got
one of these here

04:30.270 --> 04:31.670
Fancy yard signs
at his house.

04:31.672 --> 04:33.938
I hereby swear
on this stack of bibles

04:33.940 --> 04:35.607
I ain't gonna steal nothing
from the sheriff.

04:35.609 --> 04:37.810
I'm going
to the sheriff's house

04:37.812 --> 04:39.211
To steal me something.

04:39.213 --> 04:41.546
Ha ha ha!

04:41.548 --> 04:42.681
Daddy!
Get out here!

04:42.683 --> 04:44.216
I need to talk to you!

04:44.218 --> 04:45.283
I ain't in there!

04:45.285 --> 04:46.685
You hear all those
angry damn dogs?

04:46.687 --> 04:48.152
79 dogs?

04:48.154 --> 04:50.155
I recently came in
to something valuable

04:50.157 --> 04:52.290
And I needed
real security.

04:52.292 --> 04:55.494
The kind that only
79 angry dogs can provide.

04:55.496 --> 04:57.762
You broke in to the sheriff's
house, didn't you?

04:57.764 --> 05:00.098
What?
With these wild accusations.

05:00.100 --> 05:02.034
I oughta sue your ass
for slather!

05:02.036 --> 05:03.568
You swear
on a stack of bibles?

05:03.570 --> 05:05.103
I damn sure would!

05:05.105 --> 05:07.840
But my bible stack's inside
with the dogs right now.

05:07.842 --> 05:10.242
Granny, fetch me
my stack of bibles!

05:10.244 --> 05:12.711
