with the medalists.

07:46.467 --> 07:49.601
[ laughter ]

07:49.603 --> 07:52.004
For those three weeks,

07:52.006 --> 07:54.606
The eyes of the world
were on me.

07:54.608 --> 07:56.208
And 25 years later,

07:56.210 --> 07:58.343
They ain't looked back
since.

07:58.345 --> 07:59.944
Just hit that
"buy now" button,

07:59.946 --> 08:01.279
And you can be
whole again.

08:01.281 --> 08:03.348
From what little attention
I paid

08:03.350 --> 08:06.485
To your tedious tale of woe,
10 grand is a small price

08:06.487 --> 08:09.221
To pay to make
somebody very, very happy.

08:09.223 --> 08:10.689
Is there
an address on there?

08:10.691 --> 08:13.492
Maybe I might go hunt
that mother-fudger down

08:13.494 --> 08:14.693
And kill him myself!

08:14.695 --> 08:15.894
Whoa-whoa!
Sheriff!

08:15.896 --> 08:17.830
And I said keep
the mudslides coming!

08:17.832 --> 08:19.297
Yes, sir, right away!

08:19.299 --> 08:22.167
It had gd better be teeming
with marshmallows!

08:22.169 --> 08:24.769
'cause I'm anything
but "mallow" right now!

08:24.771 --> 08:27.639
[ dogs snoring ]

08:27.641 --> 08:29.774
[ rusty grunting ]

08:29.776 --> 08:32.110
Here we go.

08:32.112 --> 08:33.846
Damn it, I can't
get this thing.

08:33.848 --> 08:35.447
Alright, come on.

08:35.449 --> 08:38.050
Aw, who gives a flip?

08:38.052 --> 08:39.317
The sheriff does, daddy.

08:39.319 --> 08:40.853
And I don't know
what the hell this is,

08:40.855 --> 08:42.187
