08:48.328 --> 08:50.128
Than making money
off a good friend.

08:50.130 --> 08:51.396
Oh, so you went online

08:51.398 --> 08:52.997
And found out
it ain't worth a shit?

08:52.999 --> 08:55.934
Not one
wheat penny, goddammit!

08:55.936 --> 08:57.269
Now step aside.

08:57.271 --> 08:59.738
I invented this here
79-dog system,

08:59.740 --> 09:03.007
And I'm the only one
that can defeat it.

09:03.009 --> 09:09.013
♪♪

09:09.015 --> 09:11.750
