09:28.369 --> 09:30.469
Come on, come on.

09:32.038 --> 09:34.373
[ gasps ]

09:34.375 --> 09:35.707
[ growls ]

09:35.709 --> 09:36.975
[ shuddering ]

09:36.977 --> 09:38.711
[ snoring resumes ]

09:38.713 --> 09:40.712
[ sighs ]

09:40.714 --> 09:42.180
[ grunts ] got it.

09:42.182 --> 09:43.782
Prowler!
Prowler!

09:43.784 --> 09:45.049
Shut up, woman!
Quiet!

09:45.051 --> 09:47.852
No, no, no, no! No!

09:47.854 --> 09:49.121
[ dogs growling ]

09:49.123 --> 09:52.190
Suck it!
Ah, no! No!

09:52.192 --> 09:54.927
[ camera shutter clicking ]

09:55.996 --> 09:58.062
Help!

09:58.064 --> 09:59.998
[ yelling indistinctly ]

10:00.000 --> 10:01.333
