Prowler!

10:15.882 --> 10:19.551
Just stay here, sheriff,
I'll get it.

10:19.553 --> 10:20.819
What the hell?

10:20.821 --> 10:23.155
Oh, my god!
It's back!

10:23.157 --> 10:25.357
My baby!

10:25.359 --> 10:28.026
